係勒索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42c1748c8a966f610a76c220f2003a7e9fca7b87","tid":606203,"uid":113626,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"爭咩丫, 溝埋一齊做檸檬牛丸啦"},{"pid":"36014613e1dea93a286942b39fcdfc8c4a978889","tid":606203,"uid":4525,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:58:54.000Z","msg":"支持維他牛告返佢轉頭"},{"pid":"8132b267c98a405bd0d27c0d14fa6c729082d648","tid":606203,"uid":38988,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T09:59:00.000Z","msg":"厚顏無恥"},{"pid":"de40491c9df841a1ada55f47209c3cadc88e4220","tid":606203,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:07:03.000Z","msg":"好大量呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ef13f7e10e9756ef29debdb403f44f67e7bdb0","tid":606203,"uid":37584,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:09:04.000Z","msg":"他又指。公司合法經營，商標亦是合法，不怕被控告，又建議香港維他主動出錢收購他們，平息糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n人無恥則無敵<br />\n你老母抄完人仲想光明正大再掠多筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db6252e46c878133d3d0669eb0276399bb17758","tid":606203,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:10:00.000Z","msg":"買兩盒維他以示支持"},{"pid":"85c8fd4aa224cdf0dd91921953c65452037c2bcb","tid":606203,"uid":70846,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"諗起早兩日有新聞話中國會保護知識產權、商標同原創<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fcfd77a5307996babbb4dbd4b80d79b13e2c3da","tid":606203,"uid":99028,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:18:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6dcb43acc4c9ddf10e81b23881820a75f0b7f882","tid":606203,"uid":68556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T10:21:05.000Z","msg":"中國成日打J 嘅專利登